#

Apple Galette

60 min
$8
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 8

Allergens:

glutendairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

AmericanFrench

Course:

dessertsnack

Tags:

desserteasyfallpie

Description

A rustic apple pie that’s simple to make and bursting with flavor!

Ingredients

  • pie crust: 1 (store-bought or homemade)
  • apples: 3 (medium, thinly sliced)
  • sugar: 1/4 cup
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • butter: 2 tablespoons (diced)
  • egg (for egg wash): 1
  • milk (for egg wash): 1 tablespoon
